  "body": "Hot fix for a regression introduced in v2.9.0\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n* Support weston-terminal (missed commit in v2.9.0) (TerminalFont, Linux)\r\n* Support hyprcursor detection (#776, Cursor, Linux)\r\n\r\nBugfixes:\r\n* Fix `fastfetch --gen-config` raises SIGSEGV when `~/.config/fastfetch` doesn't exist. Regression of `2.9.0` (#778)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<details><summary>SHA256SUMs</summary><br>\r\n\r\n```\r\n31090fbc080eee282056be6d3f7bc48165fdbccccac441cec8705e70a298ac72  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.tar.gz\r\n0d2f1e3db6e0f850ed5f1b33706c0f84e04266cf6431a8a67071f769b0f38c59  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.zip\r\n5a691fce13a4a15f4b2bb9b7239e856041392ca4e18235819e4a92c6530f52b5  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.tar.gz\r\n0512f7f32c433b2efd265f69f83e4703aff57ecadcd3e99f8eb29ba60a150e54  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.zip\r\n087728a32a1b051ecc6e6ceaee17023f34a348ed05fe08a4cacc7fd48e9791ca  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.deb\r\n28646a107d3d1096cbaa2e3d21027d64fdf33a74e5679c73cfd70bc3c904ccd8  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.rpm\r\n2af365a3a090d4db30efd00e85fb30b28d69ab72c8a3937631e61234aa2f468a  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.tar.gz\r\n4608a36854eae60fd6c929750b35d5fe4201128c81bc05c78994bbeff07026de  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.zip\r\n804023cd1353cf9522bdefdcbc77d6301cf8556b4daaeef287a9a8374a9d96f5  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.deb\r\n34216b5cf2cede8d112d522c21c66ff20baabbf2c98ef14bca6401696ac74d67  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.rpm\r\n82022dd09926d4903e43d64c9c313fa5d2f75250f6ad90128a7c4de83ffeebc2  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.tar.gz\r\n020e169cd1bff8cb00816bb065a8eedbf599a544a23ee5f2d6c2533608a16c63  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.zip\r\nf171a5ff20a37441ffb8fa197fc129166208b27b3bcf9939e7f524f81c8d1a52  fastfetch-macos-universal/fastfetch-macos-universal.tar.gz\